//🔔🔔 As toh simply boleh toh "n-ary-tree" ka mtlb voh tree jiski degree "n" hai (🚫 and orr acche se mtlb ekdam sahi se boleh toh "n-ary-tree" ka mtlb voh tree jiske nodes ki capacity "n" hai. toh apn degree nhi bolenge apn capacity bolenge as degree mtlb toh voh hota hai ki node meh kitne pointer-containers filled hai. and "capacity-of-node" ka mtlb ki uss node meh kitne-no.-of-pointer-containers available hai.🚫), mtlb ess tree meh nodes ki degree {0,1,2 and atmost 3} ho skti hai, as mtlb jaruri nhi hai ki jaise 3-ary-tree hai then yaha ess tree meh kisi na kisi node ki degree "3" honi hi chahiyeh..toh esi koi baat nhi hai.. mtlb nodes-ki-degree {0,1,2 or 3} ho skti hai.. and agr esseh hai then apn uss "tree" ko "n-ary-tree" bol sktehh hai,as mtlb apn "tree" ko dekh k bol toh nhi sktehh ki yeh konsa ordered-tree hai. toh yeh upar wali baat galat hai ki apn esseh tree ko dekh k bol sktehh hai ki ess tree ki degree 2 hai , 3 hai , 4 hai etcc..etcc.. esseh tree ko dekh k apn nhi bol sktehh. as toh apnko given hi hoga or mention hi hoga ki you have this "x-degree-tree" , thus toh phir apn confimation krenge ki ohh ess tree ki degree yeh hai. toh atlast, apnko yeh baat hi dhyn rkhni hai ki apn "tree" ko dekhke yeh nhi bol sktehh ki yeh ess "tree" ki degree itni hai.  🔔🔔
// Thus toh apnne "n-ary-tree" dekha.. and ek baat phir se acche se 🗒️📓 note-krenge ki tree ki "degree" mtlb ki uss tree k nodes ki capacity mtlb eske nodes ki capacity yeh hai ki eske node meh atmost itne( no.-of-degree) childreen aa sktehh hai, or mtlb eske node k atmost(maximumly) itne childreen ho sktehh hai.. as toh koi 5-degree-tree hai then eska mtlb yeh hai ki ess tree k nodes esseh hai ki jinki capacity 5-childrens ki hai, but jaruri nhi hai ki uss tree meh sare nodes k utne hi childrens ho, mtlb atmost utne ho sktehh hai or usseh kaam bhi ho sktehh hai. ⭕⭕ thus toh "Tree" ki "degree" ka mtlb "tree" k node-type se hai ki mtlb uss "tree" k nodes kaise hai, mtlb voh nodes {1 or 2 or 3 or etc.etc..} pointer-containers contain krteh hai. as in the simple ki uss tree k nodes k kitne childrens ho sktehh hai.

// As toh "Tree" ki degree or "Tree" ki "capacity" q ki "Tree" k liyeh dono ka ek hi mtlb hai, but node k liyeh dono mtlb "degree" and "capacity" mtlb alg hota hai. thus toh "tree" ki degree toh "tree" banane wala hi decide krta hai, as mtlb "tree-degree" toh node-k-type ki hi toh hoti hai, toh apn tree k node ko dekh k easily and simply "tree-ki-degree" bata sktehh hai.

